title: Psychology may help explain why male and female serial killers differ

title_detail.value: Psychology may help explain why male and female serial killers differ

summary: Male and female serial killers tend to choose their victims and commit their crimes in different ways, which may be due to thousands of years of psychological evolution, according to researchers.
